so I can't even go inside the store!

39
00:04:07,646 --> 00:04:09,648
Jeez.

40
00:04:12,938 --> 00:04:15,292
Oh, really?

41
00:04:15,654 --> 00:04:17,909
Yeah, thanks.

42
00:04:19,335 --> 00:04:21,660
