43
00:04:22,011 --> 00:04:25,164
- Do you really mean that?
- Of course I do!

44
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:28,339
- Hey, wanna go on a date tomorrow?
- Huh?

45
00:04:28,834 --> 00:04:32,338
- We just saw each other yesterday and today!
- That's different from a date, isn't it?

46
00:04:32,338 --> 00:04:36,329
