47
00:04:37,676 --> 00:04:40,487
Because we're dating, aren't we?

48
00:04:42,186 --> 00:04:46,288
Oh...! You're right.

49
00:04:46,346 --> 00:04:51,014
What the heck, you're weird.

50
00:04:51,815 --> 00:04:53,659
You're being called.

51
00:04:56,996 --> 00:04:59,098
Ah...

52
