I'm back.

53
00:05:32,131 --> 00:05:33,595
Fine.

54
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:36,526
I'll make it the best date ever.

55
00:05:58,832 --> 00:06:01,419
- In ten seconds.
- No, stop!

56
00:06:01,443 --> 00:06:03,723
Stop it...

57
00:06:03,901 --> 00:06:06,165
- Let's wear matching outfits. Come on.
- No... I'm really fine.

58
00:06:06,165 --> 00:06:08,490
- It suits you, look!
- I don't really like orange.

59
00:06:08,515 --> 00:06:10,548
You love orange the most, don't you?

60
00:06:13,005 --> 00:06:15,073
Suzuki!

61
00:06:15,073 --> 00:06:17,075
Whoa, ah!

62
00:06:23,618 --> 00:06:29,354
- Suzuki suddenly called me out.
- What's the "point"?

63
00:06:29,354 --> 00:06:31,356
Could you say a few words?

64
00:06:31,356 --> 00:06:34,159
Hold on a second. Hey!

65
00:06:34,489 --> 00:06:37,106
There you go. Could you say a few words?

66
00:06:38,822 --> 00:06:42,534
Huh? Is this a place to get your hair cut?

67
00:06:52,010 --> 00:06:55,113
Yo~. Good work.

68
00:06:55,113 --> 00:06:57,983
Then date me!

69
00:07:00,371 --> 00:07:01,946
Okay.

70
00:07:03,671 --> 00:07:05,937
Yessss!

71
00:07:06,992 --> 00:07:11,997
Ah~ ah... I was so nervous.

72
00:07:11,997 --> 00:07:15,667
Ah~

73
00:07:21,562 --> 00:07:25,243
One month. In one month...

74
00:08:18,935 --> 00:08:24,287
"The Proper Way To Write Love"

75
00:08:26,455 --> 00:08:30,635
(Episode 2: The Way to Revenge (Date))

76
00:08:31,209 --> 00:08:32,978
Ah...

77
00:08:35,814 --> 00:08:38,677
- Oh~ You're here.
- Yep.

78
00:08:38,794 --> 00:08:41,653
- Where are we going? Where?
- Just follow me.

79
00:08:41,653 --> 00:08:43,989
- What's up?
- Did you come up with a plan?

80
00:08:43,989 --> 00:08:47,164
- Of course.
- Nice~!

81
00:08:47,993 --> 00:08:49,560
Oh, you!

82
